Sunaj Assassin
A secret Atlantean order of killers who hunt practitioners of magic. Sunaj
conceal their Atlantean identity and operate in shadow, using espionage skills
and magic tattoos to reach targets other assassins cannot. Requires 10 kills
and Atlantean faction 200 to unlock.

Starting skills: Detect ambush, intelligence, tracking, surveillance systems,
disguise, impersonation, prowl, detect concealment, plus elective picks from
Espionage, Physical, Rogue, and Technical categories.

Attribute requirements: IQ 12, ME 12, PP 14.
Starting equipment: Atlantean combat armor in dark colors, concealed blade and
two sidearms, forged identity documents, and a kill ledger.
Starting credits: 500 credits (standard kit).
PPE / ISP: Base PPE 25, +6 per level. No starting ISP.

